1 by the employer in whose employment the employee was injured OR LAST EXPOSED, or
2 the employer’s insurer.
3 (4) Subject to any right of the Subsequent Injury Fund to be impleaded or
4 any right of the Subsequent Injury Fund to defend in a case involving payment from the
