9 paragraph (3) of this subsection.
10 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall be construed to
11 apply only prospectively and may not be applied or interpreted to have any effect on or
12 application to any claim arising from events occurring before the effective date of this Act.
13 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
14 October 1, 2026.

